data.title: Harold Wilson Service Details - Derby, Kansas
data.meta_description: MULVANE - Harold G. Wilson, age 87, retired farm worker, passed away Tuesday, October 25, 2016. No visitation. Graveside service 10 am Friday, October 28, El Paso Cemetery, Derby. Harold is preceded in death by his parents, Grover & Vernia Wilson; 2 brothers, and 4 sisters. Survivors include his brother, Raymond Wilson, of Cherokee, OK; nephews, R.C. Wilson, of Cherokee, OK, David Wilson, of Dallas, TX, and Doug Wilson, of San Marcos, TX; niece, Kay Antle, of Urich, MO; several nieces and nephews and great-nieces and great-nephews. A memorial has been established with Good Shepherd Hospice, 7829 E. Rockhill, Ste 403, Wichita, KS 67206 Friday, October 28, 2016 10:00 AM Get Directions on Google Maps
